data.Name: NOTHING TO DECLARE
data.Bio: NOTHING TO DECLARE is an Alternative rock band from Tokyo. The band was founded in 2005 in Singapore as Mas Kimura’s solo project during his earlier music career as a member of Pug Jelly/Saw Loser (Universal). Soon after the formation, NOTHING TO DECLARE released “Nothing To Declare Ep” which quickly rocketed this project onto a headlining slot in Singapore’s biggest outdoor rock festival BayBeats (70,000pax/3 days). The band then set out an array of shows that very same year capped by a nationwide tour of Japan Read more on Last.fm
